            <div type="l">
                <column>5</column>
                <head>From the Charlottesville Advocate</head>
                <origin>Charlottesville Advocate</origin>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer>Several Slave-Holders</trailer>
                <names/>
                <summary>Slaves from Albemarle have been committing crimes in Rockingham and Augusta
                    counties, and their owners agree that they should be punished and imprisoned
                    until owners pay a fee to get them out.</summary>
            </div>
